index <- yearmon(traffic2$year + ((traffic2$t - 1) %% 12) / 12)
tr2 <- zoo (traffic2 %>% 
              select(totacc, fatacc, prcfat, beltlaw, spdlaw, totacc, wkends, unem),
            order.by = index)
model_1 <- dynlm(log(totacc) ~ trend(totacc) + season(totacc), data = as.ts(tr2))
summary(model_1)
